EOL version 0.0.2

This module aids in the conversion of text file newline characters within the context of other perl code. There are several choices a user can specifiy; see POD for details on usage. A command line executable which utilizes this module is also included.

After install:

 perldoc EOL.pm
 perldoc eol


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


Alternatively, to install with Module::Build, you can use the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install



DEPENDENCIES

None.


